(238, '2021-07-20', 31, 21, 36, 23, 5, 'SSD TEAM GROUP GX2 2.5 1To', 5, 'T253X2001T0C101 ', 'GX2 2.5 1To', 399.000, 0.000, 1, '<p><strong>Interface&nbsp;</strong>SATA III 6 Gb/s -&nbsp;<strong>Capacit&eacute;&nbsp;</strong>1 To- <strong>Tension </strong>DC + 5 V -&nbsp;<strong>Temp&eacute;rature de fonctionnement</strong>&nbsp;0 &deg; C &agrave; 70 &deg; C -&nbsp;<strong>Temp&eacute;rature de stockage</strong>&nbsp;-40?C &agrave; 85?C -&nbsp;<strong>T&eacute;raoctet </strong>&eacute;crit&nbsp;1 To /&gt; 800 -&nbsp;<strong>Performance&nbsp;</strong>ATTO / <strong>Crystal Disk Mark</strong>: 1 To <strong>Lecture</strong>: jusqu&#39;&agrave; 530 Mo / s Max; <strong>Ecriture</strong>: 480 Mo / s -&nbsp;<strong>Dimensions&nbsp;</strong>100 (L) x 69,9 (L) x 7 (H) mm -&nbsp;<strong>Humidit&eacute;&nbsp;</strong>0 &deg; C ~ 55 &deg; C / 5% ~ 95% HR, sans <strong>condensation </strong>-&nbsp;Vibration&nbsp;20G (hors fonctionnement) -&nbsp;<strong>Choc&nbsp;</strong>1 500G -&nbsp;MTBF&nbsp;1 000 000 d&#39;heures -&nbsp;<strong>Syst&egrave;me op&eacute;rateur&nbsp;Windows</strong>, MAC OS 10.4 +, <strong>Linux </strong>2.6.33 +</p>\r\n', '<p style=\"text-align:center\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"40\" src=\"/ckfinder/userfiles/images/marque/408.jpg\" width=\"235\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>4 times faster. When your old computer is running slow, do you feel that it is dragging down your efficiency? With great performance and ultra-fast read and write speed, GX2 solid state drive is 4 times faster* than the traditional hard drive. It can not only speed up boot time, shutdown time and the response time of applications but also lightweight and easy to carry. It is absolutely the best product to replace the traditional hard drive. High efficiency read/write performance gives you more with less. GX2 SSD offers more efficient data read/write performance, lower power consumption, and a quiet operation experience. The problem of poor performance of most PCs is not caused by poor CPU performance, but by the slow read speed of the general hard drive. Upgrading to GX2 SSD can breathe new life into your PC by speeding up its boots/shutdown time and enhancing multi-tasking performance. Low power consumption for longer use. GX2 SSD supports a new generation of power saving technology: DevSleep (Device Sleep Mode). It features ultra-low power consumption, which turns off the power of the SATA interface when the computer goes into standby mode. It saves more battery power and extends battery life, so you can back to work mode in no time. Trustworthy and reliable. GX2 solid state drive&rsquo;s built-in smart algorithm management mechanism has functions such as garbage collection, which is able to ensure operational efficiency and prolong the service life of the SSD. Meanwhile, the powerful Wear-Leveling technology and ECC (Error Correction Code) function can enhance the reliability of data transfer.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/ckfinder/userfiles/files/Produit%202.0/5e36cac659c5e047929314.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 0, 1, 1, 0, 0, 0),
