(309, '2021-07-26', 31, 24, 51, 3, 6, 'MSI GF63 - I5-10300H | GTX 1650 TI | 8GB | 15.6', 5, 'GF63 - I5-10300H', '10SCSR-1202XFR', 2499.000, 0.000, 2, '<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Pc portable MSI GF63 Thin (10SCSR-1202XF) </strong></li>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;Processeur i5-10300H&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;Carte graphique: GTX 1650 Ti MQ 4 GB</li>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;Ecran: FHD 15,6 144 HZ IPS</li>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;M&eacute;moire: 8 GB</li>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;Disque Dur 512 GB SSD NVMe</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<p style=\"text-align:center\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/ckfinder/userfiles/images/marque/msi.png\" width=\"188\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:20px\"><strong>PC PORTABLE GAMER MSI GF63 THIN 10SCSR-1202XF</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>le PC portable Gamer<a href=\"https://fr.msi.com/Laptop/GF63-Thin-10SX-GTX/Overview\">&nbsp;</a><strong><a href=\"https://fr.msi.com/Laptop/GF63-Thin-10SX-GTX/Overview\" target=\"_blank\">MSI GF63 Thin</a>&nbsp;10SCSR</strong>&nbsp;offre d&#39;excellentes performances gr&acirc;ce &agrave;&nbsp; son &eacute;cran Full HD 144 Hz, son clavier gamer r&eacute;tro&eacute;clair&eacute; et son syst&egrave;me audio.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Le PC portable MSI GF63 Thin 10SCSR-1202XFR est caract&eacute;ris&eacute; par son processeur&nbsp;<strong>Intel Core i5-10300H</strong>, ses<strong>&nbsp;8 GB de m&eacute;moire DDR4</strong>, sa puce graphique&nbsp;<strong>NVIDIA GeForce GTX 1650 Ti (Max-Q)&nbsp;</strong>et son&nbsp;<strong>SSD M.2 PCIe de 512&nbsp;GB</strong>.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/ckfinder/userfiles/files/Produit%202.0/maxresdefault%20(12)(2).jpg\" width=\"900\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<h2><strong>Les caract&eacute;ristiques:</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>- Type :&nbsp;<strong>Ordinateur Potable Gamer</strong>.<br />\r\n- Couleur :&nbsp;<strong>Noir</strong>.<br />\r\n- Syst&egrave;me d&#39;exploitation :&nbsp;<strong>FreeDOS</strong>.<br />\r\n- Processeur :&nbsp;<strong>Hexa-Core</strong>.<br />\r\n-